    "name": "Langtang Valley Trek",
    "slug": "langtang-valley-trek",
    "description": "The Langtang Valley Trek is a beautiful Himalayan journey located north of Kathmandu near the Tibetan border. Known for its stunning mountain scenery, peaceful trails, traditional Tamang villages, and rich Buddhist culture, this trek offers an authentic trekking experience away from crowded routes. Trekkers pass through lush forests, waterfalls, alpine meadows, and yak pastures while enjoying breathtaking views of Langtang Lirung and surrounding peaks. The trek also includes visits to Kyanjin Gompa, glaciers, and local cheese factories, making it a perfect adventure for nature and culture lovers.",
